Package: lmustatdown
Title: An updated R Markdown thesis template using the bookdown package for LMU Munich, Department of Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yichen", "Han", email = "yichen.han@campus.lmu.de", role = c("aut")),
    person("Chester", "Ismay", email = "chester.ismay@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Nick", "Solomon", email = "nick@nicksolomon.me", role = "aut"),
    person("Shir", "Dekel", email = "shirdekel@yahoo.com.au", role = "ctb"))
Description: Using the bookdown package and LaTeX and Word thesis templates from
    LMU Munich, this package aims to encourage reproducible research using
    simple Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots
    and analyses as well.
Maintainer: Yichen Han <yichen.han@campus.lmu.de>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr,
    here,
    R.utils
Suggests:
    remotes,
    usethis
